# 📚 Come Back Study

**Come Back Study** ek educational website hai jo Class 6 ke students ko NCERT (Ganita Prakash) ke solutions asaan bhasha mein provide karti hai.

## 🚀 Features
- **Chapter-wise Solutions:** Maths Chapter 1 se lekar 14 tak ke saare sawal.
- **Easy Explanations:** Har pattern ko asaan diagrams ke saath samjhaya gaya hai.
- **Support Section:** Direct donation aur UPI support option.

## 🛠️ Tech Used
- **HTML5**

